REMASTERSYS

    Is a tool to remaster your system. It can make a full system backup or
    a distributable copy.
    
    Originally created by Tony "Fragadelic" Brijeski on February 12th, 2007.
    Last version released was 3.0.0 on January 11th, 2013.
    
    Forked by Daniel "Nerun" Rodrigues on October 9th, 2013.

